Django 1.4 project template
A custom project layout for Django 1.4.
Features:
   Project specific apps are stored in the apps directory.
   Project specific static media are stored in the assets directory.
   Base template and blocks
   Reset, print, and IE stylesheets
   Settings are split up into their own package named settings
      settings.base - contains common settings for the project
      settings.dev - development settings
      settings.prod - production settings
    manage_dev.py - shortcut for development that point DJANGO_SETTINGS_MODULE to the settings.dev module


Add a .env file with your DJANGO_SETTINGS_MODULE and PYTHONPATH.
.env should not be checked into source control. There is a .gitignore rule to block it.
